    &lt;span style="color: rgb(8, 51, 76); display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Note: Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted for further evaluation.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
