  <entry>
    <title>Difference Between normal SEO and local SEO marketing</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://www.webshure.com/types-of-seo-marketing" />
    <link rel="enclosure" type="image/png" href="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/webshure-1--2882-29.png" length="1271671" />
    <author>
      <name />
    </author>
    <updated>2023-01-23T12:57:51Z</updated>
    <published>2023-01-23T12:57:51Z</published>
    <content>&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;h1&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(8, 51, 76);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Understanding the Difference between Normal SEO and Local SEO Marketing
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/SEO" style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Search engine optimization
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            (SEO) is a crucial aspect of digital marketing, including
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           SEO marketing
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            , that helps businesses improve their visibility and drive more traffic to their
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Website" style="display: unset;" target="_blank"&gt;&#xD;
      
           website
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           . However, there are two main types of SEO: normal SEO and local SEO. In this blog post, we'll explore the difference between the two and why it's important to understand the distinction.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/10-c3cc30dd.png" alt="Normal SEO Marketing (see image)"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; text-align: left; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(89, 158, 202);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Normal SEO Marketing
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            Normal
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Search_engine_optimization" style="display: initial;" target="_blank"&gt;&#xD;
      
           SEO
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           , also known as national or global SEO, is the process of optimizing a website to rank higher in search engine results pages (
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Search_engine_results_page" style="display: initial;" target="_blank"&gt;&#xD;
      
           SERPs
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           ) for relevant keywords on a national or global level. This type of SEO is focused on improving the visibility of a website for a broad audience, regardless of their location.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/webshure+1+%2883%29.png" alt="Local SEO Marketing (see image)"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; text-align: left; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="color: rgb(89, 158, 202); display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Local SEO Marketing
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/local-seo" style="display: unset; font-weight: normal;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Local SEO
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: normal;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           , on the other hand, is the process of optimizing a website to rank higher in search engine results pages (SERPs) for relevant keywords on a local level. This type of SEO is focused on improving the visibility of a website for a specific geographical area, such as a city or region.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/webshure+1+%2884%29.png" alt="The main difference between normal SEO and local SEO Marketing (see image)"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; text-align: left; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; display: unset; color: rgb(89, 158, 202);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           The main difference between normal SEO and local SEO Marketing
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           The main difference between normal SEO and local
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            SEO Marketing
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is the scope of the audience and the geographical area being targeted. While normal SEO focuses on reaching a broad audience, local SEO is focused on reaching a specific, local audience. This means that local SEO is more focused on targeting local keywords, getting listed in local directories, and building local citations and backlinks.
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            There are some key elements that businesses should consider when implementing local SEO, such as creating and optimizing
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://goo.gl/maps/GMrMF2qvgYWUpzxf9" target="_blank" style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Google My Business
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            listing, getting listed in local directories, building local citations, and encouraging customer reviews.
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/37-2ad66bda.png" alt="SEO vs. Local SEO marketing Conclusion (see image)"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; text-align: left; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; display: unset; color: rgb(89, 158, 202);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Conclusion
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            In conclusion, the main difference between normal
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           SEO
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            and local
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           SEO
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is the scope of the audience and the geographical area being targeted. While normal SEO is focused on reaching a broad audience,
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            local SEO
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is focused on reaching a specific, local audience. Understanding the distinction between the two is crucial for businesses to effectively target their audience and improve their search engine rankings through
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           SEO marketing
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;</content>
    <summary type="text">Understand the key differences between normal SEO and local SEO marketing. Improve your website's visibility and target the right audience effectively.</summary>
    <g-custom:tags type="string">Local SEO,SEO</g-custom:tags>
    <media:content medium="image" url="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/webshure-1--2882-29.png" />
