    <title>Google's Mobile-First Approach: Boost Your Rankings with  Mobile Friendly Websites</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://www.webshure.com/mobile-friendly-websites" />
    <link rel="enclosure" type="image/png" href="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/webshure+1+%2878%29.png" length="2126231" />
