      <name />
    </author>
    <updated>2023-01-01T18:56:30Z</updated>
    <published>2023-01-01T18:56:30Z</published>
    <content>&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;h1&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Unlock the Power of a Mobile Friendly Website: Why Your Site Needs to Adapt to the Mobile Age
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;h2&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="color: rgb(89, 158, 202); display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Why Your Website Must Be Mobile Friendly and How Google Ranks Them?
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            In today's digital age, having
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            mobile friendly websites
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is no longer an option - it's a necessity. With more and more people accessing the internet on their
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smartphone" style="display: unset;" target="_blank"&gt;&#xD;
      
           smartphones
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            and tablets, it's crucial that your website can adapt to these different devices. Here's why your website must be mobile friendly and how
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            Google ranks
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           them.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/webshure-1--283-29.png" alt="Mobile friendly websites"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/2-3ac88976-8b6e9148.png" alt="a mobile phone"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            First, let's talk about why
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           mobile friendly websites
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is so important. Simply put, mobile devices are becoming the primary way that people access the internet. In fact, according to Statista, as of October 2020, over 52% of all website traffic worldwide was generated through mobile phones.
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            This means that if your
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Website" target="_blank" style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           website
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is not optimized for mobile, you could be missing out on a huge portion of your potential audience. Additionally, a mobile friendly website ensures that your visitors have a good user experience, regardless of the device they're using. A website that is difficult to navigate or doesn't display correctly on a
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           mobile device
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            will likely discourage visitors from staying on your site and could lead to a high bounce rate.
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            Now, let's discuss how
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Google ranks mobile friendly websites
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           . Google has stated that they use a "
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           mobile-first
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            " index, which means that the mobile version of a website is used to determine its ranking in search results. This means that if your
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/ai-websites-old1" style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           website
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is not
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           mobile friendly
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           , it could be at a disadvantage when it comes to search engine optimization (
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/SEO" style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           SEO
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           ). Additionally, Google has also announced that starting in 2021, they will be using a new algorithm that will give a boost in rankings to the websites that are fast loading, visually stable and mobile friendly.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/3-c90b4c60-d8011b22.png" alt="ranking 1ste on Google"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/webshure+1+%2876%29.png" alt=""/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;h2&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; color: rgb(255, 126, 2);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           DID YOU KNOW ?
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; text-align: left; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(255, 126, 2);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           6.8 Billion
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           people are using smartphones In 2023. It is also 3.2 billion, or 86.5%, more than the number of smartphone users there were in 2016, just seven years ago. In fact, from 2016 to 2023, the total number of global smartphone users grew at an average of 9.5% annually, with the biggest growth coming in 2017. That year, the number of smartphone users grew by 20.9%.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="text-align: left; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://www.oberlo.com/statistics/how-many-people-have-smartphones" style="display: unset; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           https://www.oberlo.com/statistics/how-many-people-have-smartphones
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/webshure-1--2877-29.png" alt="Google's mobile-first index"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; text-align: left; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            In conclusion, having
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           mobile friendly websites
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is essential for reaching and engaging with your target audience.
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Google's mobile-first index
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            and new algorithm also make it clear that a mobile friendly website is crucial for
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/seo-services-in-Germiston" style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           SEO
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            success. If your website is not yet mobile friendly, it's time to make the switch. By optimizing your website for
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           mobile devices
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           , you'll ensure that your visitors have a good user experience and that your site has the best chance of ranking well in search results.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;</content>
