  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            Search engines like Google, Yahoo! Bing, Yandex etc. consider fresh and relevant content as a ranking factor. To meet their criteria and stay on top of search results, you need to be adding fresh content regularly. Consider a daily, weekly and monthly schedule. So it’s really important that you can update your own site content and add new pages independently. The easiest way to keep your site regularly updated is by facilitating a weekly blog, and hiring a
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Websites design Johannesburg
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
