    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            Mobile Responsiveness:
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            With the increasing use of
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           mobile devices
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            to access the internet, it is essential that your website design is
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           mobile-friendly
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: unset;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            . This means that your website should be optimized for viewing on smaller screens and be easy to navigate with a touch screen. As a
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
