    <published>2020-12-29T06:03:46Z</published>
    <content>&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;h1&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; color: rgb(8, 51, 76);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Are you a social media addict?
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; color: rgb(8, 51, 76);"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial; color: rgb(8, 51, 76);"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;h1&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; color: rgb(8, 51, 76);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Web designers Johannesburg
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/photo-1562577309-4932fdd64cd1-6e0920d0+2.webp" alt="Web designer johannesburg"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/photo-1562577309-4932fdd64cd1-6e0920d0.jpg" alt="Web designer johannesburg (see image)"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            Do you find yourself on Facebook, YouTube or TikTok or any other
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/social-media-manager-old" style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           social platform
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            wondering where the last hour has gone? Worse than that, when using social media, are you telling yourself that you are actually busy “researching” or “working on
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           social media
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            ”, or any other of the many things we say to ourselves, but really we know we should be taking action instead?
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/home-old" style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Webshure
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is your
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Web designers Johannesburg
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           .
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
            
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           I know the answer is probably YES, because most of us are guilty of this to a certain extent when we have a social media account of some sort. Don’t get me wrong, social media has real merit, especially for digital marketers/
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Web designers Johannesburg
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/home-old" style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Webshure
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           , but one of the most difficult things about social media is noticing when it becomes a “problem” stopping you from getting stuff done.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
            
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_media" target="_blank" style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Social media
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            algorithms are designed to engage you and keep you locked into their platform. It’s becoming a serious problem for a lot of people and will seriously hinder how much they get done if they don’t control it, or admit it’s a problem. 
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
            
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            So in the spirit of the theme of this message, I’m going to give you three tips you can implement immediately, “right now”, instead of spending time reading a long
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blog" target="_blank" style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           blog
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            when you could be taking action! This is recommended by many top
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-style: italic;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           entrepreneurs
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           , so don’t dismiss it, just do it!
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
            
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            1.   Firstly turn off the notifications on your
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           social media
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            . Control your
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/mobile-app-development-old" style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           social media
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            instead of it controlling you. The constant pinging of your phone is like crack, sucking you into the screen with the fear of missing that next piece of viral content. Turn them off!
            &#xD;
        &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
        &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            2.    Commit to becoming a contributor not consumer on social. Posting to your target audience regularly, both in terms of actual posts and stories, reels etc. There’s plenty of advice out there for this to make it easy, just don’t get sucked into watching too many
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube" target="_blank" style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           YouTube
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            videos before taking action when “
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-style: italic;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           researching
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           ”!
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           3.   Then, diarise when you will be posting and responding to messages with a reminder that notifies you saying “
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-style: italic;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           social media posting/research/replies
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           ” (I have this twice a day, once in the morning , once in the evening). If you want to consume, set time aside and set an alarm to prompt you when time is up.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            These may appear extreme to you, but if they do, remember for most addicts, denial is the first stage! If you want to find out more about how to implement this or any other strategy, book on a call with
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Webshure, the Web designers Johannesburg.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
            
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           If becoming a super successful entrepreneur is your dream, diary management like this is vital. These three steps could be the tips that help you get much more done towards your goals. Let’s start working on that business or making a decision as to what business you are going to start, instead of falling down the rabbit hole that is a real social problem.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
            
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            So what are you waiting for?
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Web designers Johannesburg
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            is the solution,
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
