  <entry>
    <title>10 Tips for the Most Imaginative Website Design with AI.</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://www.webshure.com/most-imaginative-website-design" />
    <link rel="enclosure" type="image/jpeg" href="https://irp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/md/unsplash/dms3rep/multi/photo-1559854036-4ca3445a51b7.jpg" length="128825" />
    <author>
      <name />
    </author>
    <updated>2020-05-03T14:32:31Z</updated>
    <published>2020-05-03T14:32:31Z</published>
    <content>&lt;h1 style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&#xD;
    
          10 Tips for the Most Imaginative Website Design. 
         &#xD;
  &lt;/font&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  
         If you would like to develop your company on the World Wide Web, then it's necessary to do a creative
         &#xD;
  &lt;i&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           website design.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/i&gt;&#xD;
  
         This will allow people to visit our website and gather the information about your services and products. The saying goes that the first impression is the lasting impression and your website is the first impression to your prospective clients.
         &#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
          It's essential to create a more creative
          &#xD;
    &lt;i&gt;&#xD;
      
           website design
          &#xD;
    &lt;/i&gt;&#xD;
    
          for first impression on your client's mind so they want to visit your site again. To design the most creative website, follow the below tips.
         &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/md/unsplash/dms3rep/multi/photo-1499951360447-b19be8fe80f5.jpg" alt="Website design should look this good. (See the picture)"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           1. About us Page in the website design.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/join" style="font-weight: bold; display: initial; color: rgb(81, 164, 254);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Contact us
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            page is also advisable to start a relationship among you and your clients. You must therefore give your email address so visitor can contact you directly and you can give unlimited support. About us page must be included in the
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           web design
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            to provide the information about your company, people want to know who they dealing with. The information can be year of establishment, your growth, and name of country from where you operate.
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="/" style="display: initial; color: rgb(81, 164, 254); font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Home page
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            must be included with links to all the other WebPages. All web pages must be linked to the Home page for easy navigation.
            &#xD;
        &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           2. Attractive Website design
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Your website should be attractive. The colour selection for your pages has to look good, need to have a modern look and feel. The colour of the background has to be light and website design has to be appealing by a visitor first look and feel.
           &#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           3. Professional website design
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            Your website should be professional, properly titled pages and page descriptions better known as
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://www.webshure.com" target="_blank" style="display: initial; color: rgb(81, 164, 254); font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           meta descriptions
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            . The content must be placed in easy readable portions and unnecessary content must be avoided. It is important to give visitors enough information to make a decision. The
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-style: italic;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           website design
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            should be able to show the visitor's easily their interest for visiting your website. 
            &#xD;
        &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           4. Small size of web Pages in your website design.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            Web Pages should also be good looking and creative as well.  The smaller the pages and the lest content the faster the pages load. You want a
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-style: italic;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           website design
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            that are compact however have enough content to convert visitors into customers.
            &#xD;
        &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="font-weight: bold; display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           5. Text in the website design
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            The background of the webpage should be light and text should be dark, this makes for an impressive combination. To read the text easily, the background should not be dark and try to avoid dark pictures. All the fonts of the Web Pages should be chosen properly which are easily available on every font database. In other words visitors do not need to install new
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Font" target="_blank" style="display: initial; color: rgb(81, 164, 254); font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           fonts
          &#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span style="display: initial;"&gt;&#xD;
        
            in order to read the text of your webpage. They can surf and read your site's text easily..
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;img src="https://irp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/088b40b3/dms3rep/multi/Our+designed+website-s+is+the+best+with+AI.+%28see+the+picture%29.jpg" alt="designer business with a creative website design. (see the picture)"/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
    
          6. Capitalised Text in your website design
         &#xD;
  &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
          If you want to emphasise something, is the only time you should use
          &#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           capitalised text
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
    
          . Don't use capitalise text in every sentences, it is hard to read. You also may want to consider making keywords bold or italic which improves the on page SEO.
          &#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           7. Grammar in the website design.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;a href="https://yoast.com/flesch-reading-ease-score/" target="_blank"&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;font style="color: rgb(81, 164, 254);"&gt;&#xD;
        &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
          
             Flesch Reading ease
            &#xD;
        &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;/font&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    
          is a method used to determine how easily the text and sentences is read in concept and is used by search engines to rank your site. You should not be careless in the text which is written in the page it needs to make sense.  Before you publish your website design, you must read it thoroughly and make corrections if needed. Any grammatical mistakes must be corrected and spelling mistakes should be corrected as this could mean a loss in business and being found by a search engine, by something as small as a
          &#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           spelling mistake
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
    
          . 
          &#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           8. Background Images in the website design
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
          You should keep minimum background images. Generally, it makes your pages harder to view and read. To many pictures make the page look very busy. It is good to have some pictures as the saying goes some pictures is a thousand words. Do keep this to a minimum and if you use pictures make sure they are taged properly in order to help your page and
          &#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           website SEO
           &#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           9. Image Formats in website design.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
          Generally designers use three types of image formats PNG, JPEG and GIF. Let's understand the difference between these formats.
          &#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           GIF format
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
    
           is limited to 256 colours and is a lossless compression file format, a common choice for use on the Web. GIF is a good choice for storing line drawings, text, and iconic graphics at a small file size.
         &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           PNG format
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
    
           is a lossless compression file format, which makes it a common choice for use on the Web. PNG is a good choice for storing line drawings, text, and iconic graphics at a small file size but with very good quality.
         &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           JPG format
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
    
           is a lossy compressed file format. This makes it useful for storing photographs at a bigger size. JPG is a common choice for use on the Web because it is compressed. For storing line drawings, text, and iconic graphics at a bigger file size, GIF or PNG are better choices because they are lossless and smaller in size which benefit the speed of your website.
         &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
          It is handy to use a image compressor program or internet site to reduce the file size without compromising quality of the image in your website design.
         &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           10. Frames in the website design
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
          Frames are often used to keep one or more parts of a Web page static while another part of the page is scrolled or loaded. Benefits can include faster page loading and the ability to keep a navigation bar present on the visible part of the page. Most modern
          &#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           Web browsers
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
    
          support
          &#xD;
    &lt;font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&#xD;
      
           frames
          &#xD;
    &lt;/font&gt;&#xD;
    
          . Although browser support is rarely a problem, frames can present some other challenges that Web designers should be aware of:
         &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;a href="https://www.hobo-web.co.uk/website-frames/" target="_blank"&gt;&#xD;
        &lt;font style="color: rgb(81, 164, 254);"&gt;&#xD;
          
             Frames
            &#xD;
        &lt;/font&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
    
          can bury many distinct pages under one URL, essentially breaking the URL structure. Site visitors may have problems bookmarking pages they want. The lack of direct entry to particular pages may also discourage linking from other Web sites and pass along via email. Frames can also present a dilemma in terms of optimising a site for search engines
          &#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
           SEO
          &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
    
          . 
         &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p style="line-height: normal;"&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span style="display: initial; font-weight: bold;"&gt;&#xD;
      
           Was this blog insightful and do you wish to Transform your Marketing to the latest Trending Digital platform? Be apart of the only 1% in South Africa that is utilising this digital tool. 
